        Pylint Odoo plugin
        ==================
        
        Enable custom checks for Odoo modules.
        
        +-------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------------------+
        | Code  | Description                                                                                                                    | Short name                       |
        +=======+================================================================================================================================+==================================+
        | C7902 | Missing ./README.rst file. Template here: %s                                                                                   | missing-readme                   |
