        * [REF] Fix typo
        * [IMP] Add check 'create-user-without-reset-password'
        * [IMP] Support odoo tag in xml file
        * [REF] Support of 'noupdate' in check 'duplicate-xml-record-id'
        * [REF] setup.cfg: Enable ChangeLog
